AFormula NEWS -- History of user-visible changes.

Copyright (C) 2010-2011 Charles Pence.
See the end of the file for license conditions.

* Version 0.9.6 [beta]

** Update for compatibility with LLVM 3.0 APIs.


* Version 0.9.5 [beta]

** Add the atan2(y, x) function, following the C math library.


* Version 0.9.4 [beta]

** Fix a bug regarding trailing whitespace in formulas.


* Version 0.9.3 [beta]

** Add a C interface.


* Version 0.9.2 [beta]

** Fix a strange libtool bug, silencing warnings that were being received by
   linking clients.


* Version 0.9.1 [beta]

** Fix a silly bug with the SOVERSION.  Sorry!


* Version 0.9 [beta]

** Fix the backend benchmark to properly protect us from backend crashes.

** Now working with new LLVM 2.7!


* Version 0.8 [beta]

** Complete formula compilation with three backends.

** See README for basic list of features, including a full suite of binary
   operators, built-in functions, etc.



